text: S ubeddel si tazzla n ṛbeɛ ɣer uzgen n lmil, tazzla yuɣal inqes wazal-is ma d azbu yuɣal d lmeḥwiǧat tamezwarut.

Tamdint n Bikin di Ṣṣin d tamdint timestaṛḥebt s Wuraren Ulambiyen n Ccetwa di 2022, s wakka ad tuɣal d tamdint tamezwarut i yesterḥben s wuraren Ulambiyen n unebdu akked ccetwa di sin.
Tiqenṭeṛt n Yeɣẓer n Uyabuk d tiqenṭeṛt iṭṭfen s imurar. Tɛedda ɣef Iɣẓeṛ n Uyabuk iwakken ad teqqen tamdint n Uyabuk n Brazil ɣer San Ǧurǧ n Uyabuk di Tginit Taṛumit.
Amur ameqqran n lɣaci ttaṭṭafen imukan ɣef zik (imi iɣeṛṛuba ttaččaṛent s umata di tallit ideg iṭuqqut lɣaci).
Isensa n ilmeẓyen mexdumen s wudem agejdan i yelmeẓyen - inebgi s umata ittili deg iseggasen-is n snat n tmarwin - maca tzemreḍ ad tafeḍ ula d iḥewwasen imɣaren.
Amur ameqqran n ifakanen sɛan tafaska n useggas ibeddun si taggara n Wunbir arma d talemmast n Magu, i yettemxalafen aɛlaḥsab n taswast n yal afakan.
Kra n yimussnawen ɣilen d akken Itrisiratubsen ččan isikaden, d anaw n yimɣi yellan d amagnu di tallit n Ukritasi.
Γef 11:20, iɣallen n tɣellist tenna i yimeskanen ad uɣalen ɣer tneddut, s usegzi d akken ilaq ad semsawin gar uzref sεan i teskant akked tkeṛṛyas ur yezmiren ad iεeddin.
Tidyanin niḍen n uḥlucceg ɣef udfel ad ilint di temnaḍt n uḥlucceg ɣef udfel n Tayzičeng di Zhangjyaku, azal n 220km (140 n lemyal) si Bikin.
Yal win ibɣan ad irzu ɣer tmurt i yezemren ad tettuneḥsab d annar n ṭṛad ilaq-as usluɣmu amsadur.

Yarna, di tegnewt yeḥman imikruben ttimɣuṛen s lemɣawla yarna ttaṭṭafen taṛwiḥt akteṛ baṛṛa n tfekka.

Ma yella terseḍ s usexdem n yermad n daxel n uɣeṛṛabu ur tetteḥwiǧiḍ ara afiza iferqen (si 2009).
Tifin daɣen tegla-d s tikti ɣef temhazt n rric n yefrax.
Kra n yimuḍan ṭṭfen-d ahat anfafad deg uxxam n tujjya, akken ixemmem Amejjay Mull, yerna ma drus maḍi sin deg-sen d ixeddamen n uxxam n tujjya.
Ma yella truḥeḍ yiwen n ubrid kan ɣer lɣerba, imdanen zemren ahat ad sebren wa ad fehmen, zran d akken iminigen deg tmurt tabeṛṛanit ḥwaǧen ad sezgen.
Inadiyen deg imukan n uḥettec daɣen uɣalen d ineẓdamen akter deg wakud n mbeɛd 11 Cutember 2001.
Imdanen tura uɣalen ttarun tibratin ɣef lmeryat n iselkimen, mebla ma qaṛṛben ɣer teṭayitt n imru.
Inagmayen ssumren-d d akken, xas akken tagi d taseṭṭa n udinuẓur amecṭuḥ, tukkist temla-d rric n umengaḍ mačči d win n ucewcew.
Aswir n bH yettwamel-d s wakat n ibelqimen i wumi yerwi uẓṛuṛan n Hidrujen ( H di bH) deg uferdis akimiki i yettwaskeyden.
S usḥissef, mi ara txedmeḍ DVD, iran-is daɣen ad ttwakksen, dɣa ma tugna-nni tesɛa tira n usuqqel iqeṛben mliḥ ɣer yiri n wadda, ur d-ttbanent ara irkelli.
Ur d-ffiɣen ara issalen n uɛeṭṭel meqqren di tnehrawt deg ubrid ameqqran, abrid ubdil n tiɣṛemt.
Ddaw-nsen llan yemcac ilemmasen di lqed itetten tiweqqasin tilemassin i yettruḥun seg iwtal ɣer tizerzrin neɣ tidmayin.
Wekkden-d d akken ccetla n tussit n yefrax ineqqen imdanen, H5N1, tḥuza abṛik aweḥci yemmuten, i d-ufan deg wass n Arim, deg yibulmaten zdat n Lyun deg usammar n Franṣa.
Tilwiḥin n webrid kecment-d zik iwakken ad ṭṭfent iran n webrid deg umekkan-nsen. Ciṭuḥ ciṭuḥ, akken ibɣu yili, ufan-d belli iran-nni ad lhun kter lukan ad sɛun tissi n wuzzal s ufella.
Ayen ara d-iseknen s wudem amaway sem daxel n tfekka izmer ad yili d tilawt n tqerɛett n ddwa ildin neɣ tangawin takruranin isɛan sem.

D ayen i yeǧǧan tama n Ṭurk ad tili d tamurt tis 37 imeqqren akk deg umaḍal, yerna tella tamudi anect n Franṣa d Tagelda Yedduklen di snat akken.

Tazla-is tis snat, tin n inḍen imeqqranen, tekfa-t deg umḍiq wis mraw di terbaɛt n iɣimi n tlawin s wakud n tazla n 4: 41.30 , 2:11.60 s deffir n tmenzut i yekfan timzizelt Tustralit Kludya Lusc d 1:09.02 n tesint s deffir tin yeṭṭfen amḍiq wis tẓa Tahungarit Gyungyi Dani.

Mi ara tiliḍ deg imuras deg uxxam, tesɛiḍ akud ad tedduḍ i lebɣi i yiman-ik ad teṭṭfeḍ kra n dqayeq n zyada iwakken ad d-txedmeḍ taɣawsa timeẓlit.
